{"tid":1913587,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實睇GDP冇用","createTime":"2020-03-07T02:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:18:38.000Z","uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6b211070a1ab85c028e90c48bf3bc25426cc82","tid":1913587,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"GDP係本地生產總值，只能反映當年生產左咩，GNP都差不多，兩者都係指核心收入，但衡量財富當然係睇資產、金融能力、技術、知識等綜合黎睇，所以用國民總財富睇比會好啲<br />\n<br />\n例如瑞信的國民總財富，2018全球財富報告香港有15萬億，中國有52萬億，香港佔中國22%資產，而GDP只佔3%，已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dr8TMCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdr8TMCk.png&h=bc629458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9ac3d618b0f0b4ed9972f7f1fcfb01866acf7","tid":1913587,"uid":133375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"打飛機有用"},{"pid":"5975e76d70496e4e4ca699a6f8e4bf147f694d6d","tid":1913587,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"273bdf23ba3fc002dee291efb3b1d681fd424d76","tid":1913587,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef9ac3d618b0f0b4ed9972f7f1fcfb01866acf7","tid":1913587,"uid":133375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"打飛機有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"淨係支那打飛機有用姐<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}